title: Ice hockey players in Finland 2010/11 - 2017/18
summary: In general Number of players has rose over the Year.
Number of players is slightly increasing from 2011/12 to 2013/14, and finally roughly constant from 2013/14 to 2015/16.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2011/12 and 2012/13.
The highest Number of players, of value 75871.0 was reached at Year 2014/15
Minimum Number of players about 56626.0 was reached at Year 2011/12
